com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base

Class AbstractReferenceDto<F extends ReferenceDto,T extends ReferenceDto>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base.IdentifiableDto
      • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base.AbstractReferenceDto<F,T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseDto, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssociationDto, EntityReferenceDto

    public class AbstractReferenceDto<F extends ReferenceDto,T extends ReferenceDto>
extends IdentifiableDto
    Each DTO that constitutes a link/association between two entities in the system or between one entity and an external URL, must extend this class.
    See Also:
